4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp aimed at newcomers, providing a comprehensive foundation in Windows, Linux, network and server administration. Participants will learn essential skills for securing various environments, cloud security, penetration testing, and threat intelligence analysis. The program spans 16 weeks with three live online classes each week, accommodating up to 18 students per class. There are no prerequisites, making it accessible for all. Upon completion, students receive an Official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop